column2:
Exchange
1. The exchange is divided into guild auction and local auction.
2. Only players who have joined the guild can participate in the Guild Exchange.
3. All players in this server can participate in the exchange.

Guild Exchange
1. Guild exchange, participants are limited to members of the guild
2. Exchange loot comes from guild-related activities
3. When the loot is sold on the exchange, players participating in the event can receive dividends

world exchange
1. World Exchange, all players in this server can participate

Auction rules
1. Purchase of loot on the exchange, including bidding and fixed price
2. The base price of the loot is the low price of the auction, and the highest price is the fixed price.
3. At the end of the auction, the highest bidder gets the spoils
4. When the loot is purchased at a fixed price, the purchased loot is calculated immediately and is no longer subject to bidding.
5. When bidding, you need to pre-consume currency. When the bidding fails, the currency will be directly returned to the player's account or sent by email.
6. After the auction ends, the resources obtained by players' bidding will be sent in the form of emails. The guild dividends obtained can be collected by themselves in the dividend interface. If the dividends are not collected in time, they will be sent in the form of emails at 05:00 the next day.
column3:
交易所
1.交易所分為公會拍賣和本服拍賣
2.公會交易所只有加入公會的玩家可以參與
3.本服交易所本服所有玩家可以參與

公會交易所
1.公會交易所，參與人員僅限本公會成員
2.交易所戰利品來源於公會相關活動
3.交易所中戰利品售出，參與活動的玩家可以分紅

世界交易所
1.世界交易所，本服所有玩家可以參與

競拍規則
1.交易所中戰利品購買，包括競價和一口價
2.戰利品的基礎價為競價的低價，最高價為一口價
3.拍賣結束時，出價最高者獲得戰利品
4.當戰利品被一口價購買時，被購買戰利品立即計算，不再被競價
5.競價時，需要預消耗貨幣，當競價失敗時，貨幣將直接返還到玩家賬戶或是以郵件形式發送
6.拍賣結束後，玩家競價獲得的資源將以郵件的形式發送，獲得的公會分紅可以在分紅介面中自行領取，若未及時領取分紅將以郵件的形式於次日05:00發送
